OL,3,CChalet owners plan legal action in
OL,4,Choliday park council tax row
OL,6,FChalet owners at a holiday village on
OL,7,Fthe Yorkshire coast are planning legal
OL,8,Faction over claims they are unfairly
OL,9,Fbeing made to pay council tax.
OL,11,FPeople with properties at South Shore
OL,12,FHoliday Village in Bridlington say it
OL,13,Fis the only holiday park in the East
OL,14,FRiding of Yorkshire area where the
OL,15,Fcharges apply.
OL,17,FEast Riding of Yorkshire Council said
OL,18,Fit is powerless to exempt owners from
OL,19,Fthe #1,500-a-year tax.
