OL,3,CChalet owners plan legal action in
OL,4,Choliday park council tax row
OL,6,FBut some of the chalet owners, who are
OL,7,Fallowed to live in the properties for
OL,8,Fa maximum of six months a year, are
OL,9,Fnow planning to take their case to a
OL,10,Ftribunal.
OL,12,FSteph Keenan, who bought her chalet in
OL,13,FOctober 2023, said: "We don't get a
OL,14,Fwheelie bin, we don't get a bulky
OL,15,Fwaste collection, we don't get post.
