OL,6,FMs Keenan successfully appealed the
OL,7,Fdecision but was then told South Shore
OL,8,Fis the only chalet site liable for
OL,9,Fcouncil tax in the county.
OL,11,FShe added: "You think, why am I paying
OL,12,Fcouncil tax when I can't live here and
OL,13,Fit's not permanent?"
OL,15,F"It's a non-residential holiday hut, a
OL,16,Fwooden shed. Is it really worth #1,522
OL,17,Fa year to stay in a wooden shed 28
OL,18,Fdays at a stretch. Because you can't
OL,19,Fstay longer."
