OL,6,FAfter a challenge to the VOA failed to
OL,7,Freverse the tax, Ms Keenan said
OL,8,Fresidents are intending to take the
OL,9,Fissue to tribunal.
OL,11,FIn a statement the VOA said it could
OL,12,Fnot comment on individual cases.
OL,14,FIt added: "In England, to qualify for
OL,15,Fbusiness rates a self-catering
OL,16,Fproperty must be available to let for
OL,17,Fat least 140 nights and actually let
OL,18,Ffor at least 70 nights over the
OL,19,Fprevious 12 months.
